'''布拉德·加雷特'''（{{lang-en|Brad Garrett}}<ref>''California Birth Index, 1905–1995''. Center for Health Statistics, California Department of Health Services, Sacramento, California. At Ancestry.com</ref>，{{bd|1960年|4月14日||}}）是[[美國|美國]]男演員兼獨角喜劇演員，三次獲得黃金時段艾美獎。他出生在加利福尼亞<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/16/Brad-Garrett.html |title=Brad Garrett Biography (1960-)<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2016-02-27 |archive-date=2018-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180812022301/http://www.filmreference.com/film/16/Brad-Garrett.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是一位猶太人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lasvegassun.com/blogs/kats-report/2014/apr/10/its-good-times-brad-garrett/ |title=It’s good times for Brad Garrett as his Comedy Club turns 2 at MGM Grand |access-date=2016-02-27 |archive-date=2019-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190804170750/https://lasvegassun.com/blogs/kats-report/2014/apr/10/its-good-times-brad-garrett/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有兩個哥哥。他曾就讀於[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]，但入學六個禮拜之後就退學投入喜劇事業。

